---
// Illustrated cloud bank anchored to the bottom of the viewport, plus two
// small floaters drifting high in the sky. Colored entirely by the
// --cloud-hi/--cloud-lo custom properties, which sky.ts already crossfades
// continuously with the rest of the sky. No JS in this component.
---

